tagline: I want to work with people, constantly learn new tech, and apply IT to business.
body:
### Hello World
My name is Pauly Russ, and I'm a technical analyst studying information science and trying to learn as much as I can about the technical and business sides of the IT world. Right now, this simple greeting will be my placeholder as I work on what I actually want to say with this page.

### Contact
While I'm working though, you can contact me on: [LinkedIn](www.linkedin.com/in/PaulyRuss) or [Twitter](https://twitter.com/PaulyPedantic).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
